ocess if necessary with another <b>250 g<b> partially frozen meat.<br><br>IMPORTANT: do not put fully frozen meat, nor partially frozen meat in one large piece in mixing bowl because there is a risk of damage to the blades. The meat must be thawed slightly and in pieces."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","15 pieces"]}